quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  51,49,"Ni mu chindu chilichose tugumbile iŵili-iŵili (mpela chachilume ni chachikongwe), kuti jenumanja nkumbuchile (ukoto wa Allah)."
  51,50,"Basi (mwasalilani yanti): “Tililani kwa Allah, chisimu une (Muhammadi ﷺ) kukwenu ni nkutetela jwakuonechela jwakuuma Kukwakwe.”"
  51,51,"“Soni ngasim’biika pamo ni Allah nnungu jwine, chisimu une (Muhammadi ﷺ) kukwenu ni nkutetela jwakuonechela jwakuuma Kukwakwe.”"
  52,40,"Kapena mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) nkwajuga ŵanganyao malipilo, sano jamanjao ni akusitopelwa nasyo ngongole?"
  52,41,"Kapena akwete ŵanganyao (ilimu) yakusisika, basi ŵanganyao ni akulemba (yalakweyo)."
  52,42,"Kapena akusaka kutenda maliindi? Basi aŵala ŵaakufuulu ni ŵali ŵakwaujila malindi gao."
  53,34,"Ni jutosile panandi (mu chipanje chakwe) kaneka ni kuleka (kutolako)?"
  53,35,"Ana kukwakwe kwana umanyilisi wakusisika, basi jwalakwe ni jukuiona (yanti chipanje chakwecho chichimale ligongo lyakutola)?"
  53,36,"Ana nganijusalilidwa yaili mu ikalakala ya Musa?"
  54,25,"“Ana chikumbusyo chipelecheedwe kukwakwe (Swaleh jikape) sikati jetu? (Ngwamba), nambo jwalakwe ni jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya.”"
  54,26,"Tachimanyilila malaŵi kuti ana nduni jwali jwaunami kusyene, (soni) jwakulikulungusya."
  54,27,"(Twansalile Swaleh kuti): “Chisimu Uwwe tukutumisya ngamiya jekongwe kuŵa mayeso kukwao, basi mwajembechelani ni mpilile.”"
  55,19,"Aŵisile mbwani siŵili syasikusimana (jamesi gakunong’a ni jamesi gachijete)."
  55,20,"Sikati jakwe jana uŵigo, mwanti syangajinjililana."
  55,21,"Ana nichapi mu chindimba cha M’mbuje gwenu (ŵanaŵaŵili mmwe ŵandu ni majini) chankuchikaana (kuti nganichiŵa Chakwe)?"
  56,10,"Ni (pachiŵa pana soni) ŵaŵalongolele (pakutenda yambone ku duniya) ŵatachiŵa ŵakulongolela (ku Mbepo)."
  56,11,"Ŵanganyao ni ŵatachiŵa ŵakuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)."
  56,12,"Tachiŵa m’Matimbe Gachindimba (ku Mbepo)."
  57,1,"Iŵele ili nkunswejesya Allah Yosope yaili kumawunde ni petaka, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  57,2,"Uŵele Ŵakwe uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, jukupelekaga umi ni chiwa, soni Jwalakwe pa chindu chilichose juŵele Jwakombola."
  57,3,"Jwalakwe ni Jwandanda (pangali chilichose paujo Pakwe), soni Jwambesi (pangali chilichose panyuma Pakwe), soni Jwapenani kusyene (pangali chilichose pachanya Pakwe), soni Jwakuŵandika nnope (ni umanyilisyi Wakwe, pangali chakuŵandika nnope kupunda Jwalakwe), soni Jwalakwe chindu chilichose juŵele Jwaachimanya chenene."